{"tid":1468243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FACT CHECKED 機場係春袋，要大大力錫落去","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:36:45.000Z","uid":52609,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e34f36fd86abb3082123aa434ec5ac2b3ec5ef63","tid":1468243,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"812 用狼來了，恐嚇和理非唔敢入機場<br />\n813 用鬼捉鬼方式，想令和理非同勇武割蓆。防暴唔敢入T1暴力清場，只係T1外捉人<br />\n814 機場禁制令，想令和理非唔敢入<br />\n<br />\n接連三招出得咁快<br />\n證明中共真係好驚我地去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地更加要大大力錫佢春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入機場睇戲，食譚仔！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住所有手足共識：<br />\n1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼正確方法 (PR最好睇)<br />\n1. 詢問<br />\n2. 控制，防止逃跑<br />\n3. 搵記者，由記者盤問（811記者問黑警扮示威者咁樣）<br />\n4. 睇證件、影相<br />\n5. 散水，不包圍<br />\n<br />\n721 805 811"},{"pid":"2a5e9c1ba1d4fe8af807ad445398967c95fac062","tid":1468243,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲記唔記得我地嘅招降大法？？？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sing hallelujah to the lord</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有狗、有反對聲音<br />\n<br />\n用歌聲招降就夠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRhPdzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRhPdzF.png&h=626d1498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgVtt79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgVtt79.jpg&h=644fdc1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"